  <title>WebKit2.Settings.javascript_can_access_clipboard</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
Settings.javascript_can_access_clipboard: Boolean (Read / Write / Construct)
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Whether JavaScript can access the clipboard. The default value is <code>false</code>. If
set to <code>true</code>, document.execCommand() allows cut, copy and paste commands.</p>

